name: Private Ocean
description: Human life is built to be alone. To feel alone. To face "it" alone. Each mind has its own backyard, and in that backyard there is an ocean. Diving in that ocean is a one-way ticket to the deep deep depths of Self. That is why most humans play it safe in the backyard and slightly dip their toes. If only they could SEE... How magestic their insular universes are."
